headline: Campbell's Q1 Earnings Beat Estimates, Net Sales Drop 3% Y/Y
summary: CPB beats EPS estimates even as sales and margins slip, with cost pressures and a planned La Regina stake shaping its 2026 outlook.

headline: Mama's Creations Q3 Earnings Beat Estimates, Sales Rise 50% Y/Y
